title: Head-on smash between car and truck at Cooke Plains, south of Tailem Bend
text:
POLICE are at the scene of a head-on smash between a truck and a car at Cooke Plains, south of Tailem Bend.
The accident happened at the intersection of Dukes Highway and Gypsum Rd just after 2pm.
Dukes Highway has been closed to all west-bound traffic as a result of the accident.
Diversions have been put in place to the Princes Highway and Mallee Highway.
East-bound traffic will be diverted to Coomandook via the Old Dukes Highway.
